            "title": "滬指開市升12點 深成指升96點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段持續向上，上證綜指以4039點開市，升12點或0.32%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14736點，亦升96點或0.66%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升25點或0.54%，開報4726點；創業板指數開市報3596點，升37點或1.06%。</p>\n</div>",
