            "title": "港股開市︱收復兩萬六 恒指再升295點報26168點 寧德時代績前平開",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場對美伊或重啟談判的憧憬，繼續推動環球股市反彈，港股今早亦再度高開，收復兩萬六關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數開市報26168點，升295點或1.14%。恒生科技指數開報4961點，升109點或2.26%；國企指數以8776點開市，升104點或1.21%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普遍造好，滙控(00005)開報142.3元，升0.92%；友邦(01299)開報87元，暫時無升跌。阿里巴巴(09988)開報129.5元，升4.02%；騰訊(00700)開報500元，升1.38%；京東(09618)的ADR昨晚高收逾6%，該股今早在港開報122.3元，升5.98%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251230_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251230_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代(03750)昨天受配股傳聞拖累逆市報跌，公司今日將舉行董事會議決首季業績；該股今早在競價時段以660元開市，暫時無升跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兩隻藥業股相繼在今早開市前宣布配股，今早股價齊低開。基石藥業(02616)開報9.6元，跌0.42%；藥捷安康(02617)開報67.5元，跌2.95%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15874413-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a9%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e5%85%ad-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%86%8d%e5%8d%87295%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126168%e9%bb%9e-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-15 09:27:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "人民幣兌美元中間價上調11點 創逾3年新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民幣兌美元中間價報6.8582，上調11點，創自2023年3月24日以來新高；上日中間價6.8593，官方收盤價6.8164，夜盤收報6.8156。</p>\n</div>",
